  "description": "A close-up, eye-level view of the inner bloom of a pink tulip. The petals are delicately textured and gently ruffled, radiating outwards from a central point. The heart of the flower reveals dark blue stamens tipped with golden pollen surrounding a pale yellow pistil. The petals display subtle variations in shade, with hints of deeper pink and lighter, almost white areas near the edges. The background is softly blurred, suggesting the flower is in a natural setting. The lighting is soft and even, enhancing the delicate details of the flower.",
